rbundler 0.1.1
--------------

Update devtools dependency to 0.7.1 and R dependency to 2.15.1.

rbundler 0.1
--------------

NEW FEATURES

* The `bundle` function installs the package and all of it's dependencies into a
bundle library.

BUNDLE PATHS

* `bundle` installs packages into `PROJECT_PATH/.Rbundle` by default.
